Life-Expectancy Disparities Among Adults With HIV in the United States and 
Canada: The Impact of a Reduction in Drug- and Alcohol-Related Deaths Using the 
Lives Saved Simulation Model.

Althoff KN(1), Chandran A(1), Zhang J(1), Arevalo WM(2), Gange SJ(1), Sterling 
TR(3), Gill MJ(4), Justice AC(5)(6), Palella FJ(7), Rebeiro PF(3), Silverberg 
